{"tid":1771611,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［温馨提示］美國國務院同英國，都係以聯合聲明作理據支持香港抗爭","createTime":"2019-12-06T03:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T09:06:11.000Z","uid":48083,"like":67,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d93b6b8e9d2b17ef6092a9bd6d789874fe86ff58","tid":1771611,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯聲明最後說，「美國相信香港的自治、堅持法治以及對保護公民自由的承諾，是維持美國法律規定下的香港特殊地位的關鍵，也是『一國兩制』成功和香港未來穩定與繁榮的關鍵。我們敦促北京遵守其在《中英聯合聲明》的承諾，包括承諾香港將『享有高度自治權』以及香港人民將享有人權、言論與和平集會自由，&mdash;這些是我們與香港共有的核心價值」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/24773/美國-香港-24774/美政府一日兩發香港聲明-譴責暴力籲各方克制\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F24773%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-24774%2F%E7%BE%8E%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A9%E7%99%BC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E7%B1%B2%E5%90%84%E6%96%B9%E5%85%8B%E5%88%B6&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=734f7111\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/24773/美國-香港-24774/美政府一日兩發香港聲明-譴責暴力籲各方克制</a><br />\n<br />\n英國下議院報告講香港：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n We reiterate our view that the Sino- British Joint Declaration on Hong Kong is a legally binding international treaty registered at the United Nations. Its validity and implementation are of profound importance both to UK national interests and to the health of the rules-based international system. </span></span></strong>We are therefore deeply concerned by the events in Hong Kong over the last six months, which have demonstrated that Hong Kong&rsquo;s autonomy is at risk, especially in the area of the rule of law, which underpins its economy.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fpF6gbq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfpF6gbq.png&h=d81db0b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201920/cmselect/cmfaff/109/109.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpublications.parliament.uk%2Fpa%2Fcm201920%2Fcmselect%2Fcmfaff%2F109%2F109.pdf&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=9a91b1bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201920/cmselect/cmfaff/109/109.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國話聲明係歷史文件<br />\n所有支持香港既外國堅稱聲明有效<br />\n<br />\n廢聲明 = 跟敵人既方向做<br />\n有人覺得係啱？<br />\n<br />\n廢聲明，斷撚咗外國干預既主要理據<br />\n可以換咗咩番嚟？<br />\n<br />\n講乜撚主權<br />\n冇軍事配合只係打飛機<br />\n而英美為香港主動出軍同一個有核武既國家打既機會<br />\n係零<br />\n<br />\n金仔明用核彈威脅美國都未敢打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英國都拆華為都未必做到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b061adb3088e2684385293ea1da464050f390a3e","tid":1771611,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:59:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714b3f0fa0a4215079fd339a5870e02f181fbe7b","tid":1771611,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"有冇問過香港人要唔要呢張廢紙？"},{"pid":"787a3e677dea1c8de361968b941ebd6bdc52af46","tid":1771611,"uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"714b3f0fa0a4215079fd339a5870e02f181fbe7b","tid":1771611,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"有冇問過香港人要唔要呢張廢紙？"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"1. 上文講咗有重要作用，唔係廢紙<br />\n2. 香港人唔係一個個體<br />\n每人都可以有自己意見<br />\n我只係指出廢聲明係戇鳩<br />\n3. 閣下係知名三毛"},{"pid":"e7f5a64b899120ad20d329e18a8ff5e52a4b6bf7","tid":1771611,"uid":146030,"like":2,"dislike":11,"sc